---
import Button from '../ui/Button.astro';
import { contactLinks, ctaLabels, primaryCtaHref } from '../../data/siteContent';
---

<section class="section-padding cta-frame">
  <div class="container cta-frame__content">
    <p class="eyebrow">Final CTA</p>
    <h2>Start with the workflow problem, not a polished specification.</h2>
    <p>
      If your business is dealing with spreadsheet sprawl, manual handoffs, weak lead intake, or disconnected tools,
      that is enough to start a conversation. From there, we can define a practical first phase and a system that
      actually supports how your business runs.
    </p>
    <p>
      Send the current workflow, the tools involved, what is breaking, and what a successful first phase should improve.
    </p>

    <div class="hero-actions">
      <Button href={primaryCtaHref} variant="primary">{ctaLabels.primary}</Button>
      <Button href="/case-studies" variant="secondary">{ctaLabels.secondary}</Button>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-links" role="list" aria-label="Contact options">
      <a href={contactLinks.mailto} role="listitem">Email</a>
      <a href={contactLinks.whatsapp} target="_blank" rel="noopener" role="listitem">WhatsApp</a>
      <a href={contactLinks.telegram} target="_blank" rel="noopener" role="listitem">Telegram</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .contact-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .contact-links a {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
</style>
